        "client_msg_id": "23152cf7-531b-41ae-8edc-911e3056aa14",
        "text": "Here's a blog post placing my HyperDoc project in the context of Bret Victor's \"explorable explanations\", with Micrograd supplying the illustrations: <https:\/\/blog.khinsen.net\/posts\/2025\/11\/12\/explorable-explorable-explanations.html>",
